(23, '2014-07-23 00:00:00', '2014-06-30 00:00:00', '0.00', 'grand_prix.jpg', 'The fifth stop takes the Arena Grand Prix Series to North Carolina. The 30th Annual Arena Grand Prix at Charlotte takes place May 15-18, 2014 at Mecklenburg County Aquatic Center in downtown Charlotte.', '<p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:18px">The fifth stop takes the Arena Grand Prix Series to North Carolina. The 30th Annual Arena Grand Prix at Charlotte takes place May&nbsp;15-18, 2014&nbsp;at Mecklenburg County Aquatic Center in downtown Charlotte.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><img alt="omg" dir="ltr" src="http://www.usaswimming.org/_Rainbow/images/_Event%20Logos/Charlotte-GP---Arena-small.jpg" style="float:right; height:108px; width:144px" /></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:18px"><strong>**Hotel Information**</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:18px">USA Swimming has partnered with Pse Tournament Housing to provide attendees/groups with the best available rates. Hotels have bee</span></span><span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:18px">n carefully selected to ensure quality and are within close</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,lucida grande,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:18px">&nbsp;proximity to the venue(s). Rooms will book up quickly so please book well in advance. Book by phone at 888-417-6446 or view hotels and book online at:&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify"><br />\r\n<span style="font-family:lucida sans unicode,luci